    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"110050\">@Sébastien Gouëzel</span> Thanks. Do you feel I should rename <code>circleAverage_sub_sub_inv_smul_of_differentiable_on</code>?</p>",
